    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">こい</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（恋）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>わ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">しはん</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（思案）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のほかとやら　<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">あなど</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（長門）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のせとの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">いなりまち</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（稲荷町）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>　ねこもしやくしもおもしろふ　あそぶ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">くるわ</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（廓）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">はるげしき</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（春景色）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>　ここにひとりの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">さるまハし</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（猿廻し）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>　たぬき<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">いつぴき</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（一匹）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ふりすてゝ　義<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">利</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（理）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>もなさけもなき<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">なみだ</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（涙）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>　ほかにこゝろハあるまいと　かけてちかいし山の神　うちにいるのにこゝろの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">やみぢ</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（闇路）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>　さぐり／＼て　いでゝ行<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
とんとんと登る梯子の真中程で　国を去つて薩摩同志　楼に上る貧乏の春　辛抱しやんせと目に涙<lb />
<lb />
